body_html:
@maverickg : Thanks for the report. The good news is that you can ignore the WARNING message, it is advisory - I don't think there is anything wrong with your setup.

@ispirmustafa : Would you mind taking a look? I think this is coming from https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.2/tensorflow/contrib/layers/python/layers/feature_column.py#L1582 - suggesting that something in feature_column.py needs to change to address the concerns expressed by the warning log?
